name: ROCKETPULT 3D
description: Description Who doesn't dream of getting on a missile? Our game will make that happen when you can control and follow the instructions of the rings and reach the end point. And, of course in space there are also many dangers, meteorites are still floating in the sky, and you don't want to lose your life when you crash into them. Try it out! Character In the game, you will transform into a missile pilot to dodge objects and get the final score. Camera The game will be in a horizontal perspective with the missile, so you know the direction of the missile. Controls Button W A S D Space Things in game Up Left Down Right Fly Team Member: Jhon Programmer Joe  SFx, Vfx, UI Lucian Project Manager Pari Programming Assistant, Artist
